iPhone 4跟當時大部分蘋果公司的流動產品一樣，其唯一的外部數據接端也是使用30針底座連接器。

iPhone 4是第一代擁有的第二個麥克風以[[靜音機|消除噪音的]]iPhone，其位於靠近耳機插孔的設備頂部，而主麥克風位於左下方<ref name="apple iP4 phone features 1">{{cite web|url=https://www.apple.com/iphone/features/phone.html|title=iPhone 4 – Learn about phone and voicemail features|publisher=Apple|date=|accessdate=2011-08-30|archive-date=2011-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110925212356/http://www.apple.com/iphone/features/phone.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 陀螺儀及傳感器 ===
iPhone 4引入了陀螺儀傳感器，它可以檢測[[笛卡兒座標系|X，Y及Z軸]]的３軸角加速度，能夠精確計算偏航、俯仰和滾轉。陀螺儀補充了加速度計，這是一種源自原始iPhone以來一直存在的傳感器，它通過檢測３軸的線性加速度來檢測裝置的加速度，抖動，振動，振動衝擊或跌下。來自加速度計和陀螺儀合併後的數據提供了有關裝置在空間裡的６軸運動提供了詳細而準確的訊息。３軸陀螺儀與３軸加速計結合，使裝置能夠識別裝置在空間中移動的距離、速度和方向<ref name="appleinsider iP4 gyro gaming 1">{{cite web|url=http://www.appleinsider.com/articles/10/06/16/inside_iphone_4_gyro_spins_apple_ahead_in_gaming.html&page=2|title=Inside iPhone 4: Gyro spins Apple ahead in gaming|first=Daniel Eran|last=Dilger|date=2010-06-16|publisher=[[AppleInsider|AppleInsider]]|page=2|accessdate=2010-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120420014347/http://www.appleinsider.com/articles/10/06/16/inside_iphone_4_gyro_spins_apple_ahead_in_gaming.html%26page%3D2|archive-date=2012-04-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

=== 晶片與記憶體 ===
iPhone 4是由[[Apple_A4|Apple A4]]晶片驅動，該晶片由[[Intrinsity|Intrinsity]]設計<ref name="anandtech intrinsity 1">{{cite web|last=Garnesh|first=T S|title=Apple's Intrinsity Acquisition: Winners and Losers|url=http://www.anandtech.com/show/3665/apples-intrinsity-acquisition-winners-and-losers|publisher=AnandTech|accessdate=2012-07-17|archive-date=2019-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190831052917/https://www.anandtech.com/show/3665/apples-intrinsity-acquisition-winners-and-losers|dead-url=no}}</ref>，與之前的所有iPhone型號一樣由[[三星集團|三星]]生產<ref name="PCW iP4 display explained 1">{{cite web|url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/198201/iphone_4s_retina_display_explained.html|title=Apple's new iPhone 4|date=2010-06-15|publisher=TechAutos|accessdate=2010-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120828060038/http://www.pcworld.com/article/198201/iphone_4s_retina_display_explained.html|archive-date=2012-08-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。這[[系統單晶片|系統單晶片]]上系統由[[ARM架構|ARM Cortex-A8]][[中央處理器|CPU]]組成，與[[PowerVR|PowerVR SGX535]][[圖形處理器|GPU]]整合<ref name="NYT CPU battle 1">{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2010/02/22/technology/22chip.html|title=For Chip Makers, the Next Battle Is in Smartphones with better technology|first=Ashlee|last=Vance|date=2010-02-21|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2010-06-19|archive-date=2010-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100225065617/http://www.nytimes.com/2010/02/22/technology/22chip.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Apple A4晶片也適用於[[iPad|iPad]]，其額定速度為1GHz。iPhone 4的轉速尚未公佈。所有iPhone的先前型號都已經對CPU進行了[[降頻|降頻]]處理，這通常可以延長電池壽命並降低其散熱效能。

iPhone 4擁有512 MB的[[動態隨機存取記憶體|DRAM]]。額外的DRAM支援更高性能和多任務處理<ref name="ifixit iP4 RAM 1">{{cite web|url=http://www.ifixit.com/Teardown/iPhone-4-Teardown/3130/1|title=iPhone 4 Confirmed to Have 512MB of RAM (Twice the iPad and 3GS)|first=Arnold|last=Kim|date=2010-06-17|publisher=[[MacRumors|MacRumors]]|accessdate=2010-06-19|archive-date=2010-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100628052241/http://www.ifixit.com/Teardown/iPhone-4-Teardown/3130/1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 容量與微型SIM卡 ===
iPhone 4改用[[SIM卡|微型SIM卡]]（microSIM）在GSM網絡上運行，它設於裝置右側的可彈出托盤中。然而，在CDMA網絡中，電話需使用[[電子序列號|ESN]]才能連接網絡。所有以前的iPhone型號都使用一般的[[SIM卡|迷你SIM卡]]。

迷你SIM卡可能取決於運營商而無法在全球內的所有網絡運作。作為技術解決方案，用戶可以利用小刀或剪刀把迷你SIM卡修剪成為微型SIM卡，以適合置於微型SIM卡的托盤中<ref name="wired iP4 microsim 1">{{cite news|url=https://www.wired.com/gadgetlab/2010/05/sim-trim-cutting-card-down-to-microsim-size|title=Trimming a sim to micro-sim size|first=Charlie|last=Sorrel|date=2010-05-06|publisher=[[Wired_(magazine)|Wired]]|accessdate=2011-11-24|archive-date=2014-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140329210049/http://www.wired.com/gadgetlab/2010/05/sim-trim-cutting-card-down-to-microsim-size|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

iPhone 4與以前的型號一樣，所有數據都存儲於8GB、16GB或32 GB的[[快閃記憶體|快閃記憶體]]中，而非存儲於[[SIM卡|SIM卡]]。跟與以前的型號不同的是，存儲容量並不會打印在裝置背面。

